data.description: PRICE  REDUCED !!! Beautifully updated home that features off street parking for 6+ cars. Green area, nice big deck on the back and a large shed. Home offers a good size living room, extra space for an office or sitting area before entering the dining room (with  sliding doors going outside to the deck and yard)  Kitchen with wood cabinets and space for a small table and chairs. A full bath (tub and separate shower) also on 1st floor.  The second-floor features 3 bedrooms. A large Master Suite ( it has been painted recently - see pictures with and without furniture ) offers a  walking closet, and full bath. There is a sitting area, family room or office in between the 3 bedrooms. Nice hardwood floors all over the house. Central AC. House has been updated in the last 10 years.
